        %p Hi, my name is Shane Burkhart and I am a computer science major at the Missouri University of Science and Technology.  My goal is to use software and computers to solve as many real world problems as I can.  I am a passionate homebrewer, and love helping people in the community.  Whether you have questions, suggestions, or simply want to talk about brewing, email me and I will gladly respond. Cheers!
