        %h3 Ryan Endacott
        %p.lead.muted Co-Founder
        %p  Hi, I'm Ryan. I've been coding for a few years, working with everything from machine learning to countless web applications.  In short, I'm excited to be building HomeBrewster and can't wait to get some awesome recipes shipped to the brewing community. Have any questions, comments, concerns, or new ideas for HomeBrewster?  Feel free to shoot me an email. Cheers and happy brewing!
